*   ## **_PETE DUNNE DEF. SHEAMUS_**
    

Sheamus and Dunne have a really stuff back and forth. Sheamus does take most of the match as the larger opponent, until Dunne tries to use a sheleighly.

The ref catches him, and Dunne uses a Cricket Bat instead 🏏

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/76afbe99-228e-4743-b987-89974a86c9e3/20240916_173656.jpg?format=original)

Jey Uso is talking to Rhea and Damien when Xavier Woods walks up and makes amends with Damien and Rhea.

Woods says he's gonna be fighting Judgement Day for the WWE TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS. Priest says New Day better make sure they get those titles tonight

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/752730a6-a935-434f-a61b-cb48da96fba0/20240916_174528.jpg?format=original)

Miz is offended Braun Strowman told him he couldn't take Bronson. Strowman shows Miz the injury Bron left him with and says he meant no offense. He's just a big monster and Miz is not.

