![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a19342f3-1e42-4cba-8b12-314d00646850/processed_20240916_174550.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_NATALIA DEF. ZOEY STARKS_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6108c6e8-7d80-4264-ad6c-c3ffd9f856b2/20240916_180543.jpg?format=original)

Jey Uso is out for a match with Strowman but he's interrupted by Bron Breakker. Breakker tells Jey Uso they're different because Bron didn't need no Bloodline. No cousins. No uncles.

The only family Bron needs is the Intercontinental Championship. He fights for the title and the title fights for him(?)

The IC title match is made official for next week. Bron snuffs Jey, USO goes down and Bron tries to hit the rebound spear but Jey Uso gets him with a spear first.

