"IM TIRED OF THIS.... SOMETHING’S GOTTA CHANGE, MAN."

XAVIER WOODS HAS WALKED OUT ON KOFI KINGSTON

*   ## **_WWE TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS: JUDGEMENT DAY DEF. THE NEW DAY_**
    

New Day was looking good until the rest of Judgement Day came out to distract Kofi. Kofi leaves the ring, the ref leaves the ring. JD and Finn jump Xavier.

JD puts Xavier in a chokehold, Finn hits the stomp at the same time. Kofi comes back after it's over but it's too late and Xavier has had ENOUGH

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/49788d71-1d6f-401c-92d9-0ee16f7c12b8/20240916_183529.jpg?format=original)

Xavier Woods is backstage screaming at the LWO for coming down and brawling with the Judgement Day during their tag team championship match. Woods says they cost him the tag titles.

Kofi walks up and let's Woods know Kofi asked them to come. Xavier ask why the hell would Kofi not TELL HIM??!

DOES KOFI THINK THE NEW DAY IS NO GOOD WITHOUT BIG E? Kofi doesn't get to respond, Woods walks off.

