![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6a246635-e8a1-41bc-8c50-3dd4461fb864/20240916_184841.jpg?format=original)

THAT WAS FREAKING AWESOME 😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭

BRAUN STROWMAN VS BRONSON REED GOES TO A NO CONTEST AFTER AN INCREDIBLE BRAWL

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3a542b19-f673-45a0-aa55-381e77fc5bf6/20240916_190523.jpg?format=original)

Sami Zayn comes out to call Gunther out for ducking him since Sami beat him at Wrestlemania. But Ludwig Kaiser will not let anybody disrespect his bro like this.

Kaiser asks what does Sami even think he's doing asking for World Title shots? Why would Gunther be scared of Sami when he's the most dominant force in the company.

If anything, Gunther is trying to protect him from a beat down. Sami wants to talk about WrestleMania but miracles never happen twice and Sami will never ever beat GUNTHER again.

Sami asks why isn't Gunther out here himself? Gunther doesn't need Kaiser to speak for him. Gunther doesn't need Kaiser for anything at all But Sami actually doesn't think Kaiser needs GUNTHER either.

Kaiser turned on Vinci to stand on his own two feet, like anybody else. But does he think he's gonna get respect being Gunther's mouth piece?

If KAISER wants to talk to Sami, he doesn't need to speak through GUNTHER. He should grow some balls and speak for himself.

GUNTHER has heard enough. He walks up to his own friend Kaiser and asks if Kaiser has anything to tell him? He should say it right now.

Kaiser says he does have something to say and he's been trying to get it off his chest for a very very long time...

Then he attacks Sami. They tell Sami the answer is still no. Gunther leaves but Sami knocks Kaiser out of the ring and stands tall in the end.

